{"tid":1495657,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[BNO值得重溫] 當年居英權論壇","createTime":"2019-08-22T07:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T17:06:34.000Z","uid":278283,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9dfa833f9824149e29815a80d2e818ead5578e","tid":1495657,"uid":278283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5KBF2lY0l1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5KBF2lY0l1U&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGITRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=41a2d24e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5KBF2lY0l1U</a><br />\n<br />\n當年英國外相賀維爵士堅持認為英國下議院絕對無可能贊成收容325萬香港人，論壇上，很多熟悉的港人面孔曾經理性發言，可惜亦無慟於衷。提醒大家，今天爭取BNO平權，面對阻力比當年更大，實在需要付出比當年更大的努力，才有成功的機會。<br />\n<br />\n今天，就由簽名開始<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGITRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=8fa8afe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"d789bb6398a687114a33987760398d2259874da0","tid":1495657,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1bb7a8ad825380ed46d844cda02703a064228f","tid":1495657,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba2a358ab7628060127a9523e557a77376d4335","tid":1495657,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"【集思廣益 ‧ 歡迎批改】《維多利亞港民主及人權宣言》- 「對抗中共極端民族主義」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495658</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，草擬左呢份宣言，岩唔岩用就唔知啦，希望8.31  可以有一份新宣言用<br />\n行文或有不當及錯字歡迎大家改善。<br />\n<br />\n知識有限，唔係好識寫可能太集中背景，中國威脅論寫唔到太多，求大神補充<br />\n排華行動可以再多啲提議<br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇到蘋果話唔可以再提升到國際層面，要求冷處理，<br />\n我地唔可以俾佢咁做，我地要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3807bb9202a2a035b50c3378f78b9314c3dcca7a","tid":1495657,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"090c12663b89f6262a9629835301ae228c0ff18f","tid":1495657,"uid":278283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"當時Live直播，代表英國倫敦既市民大部分都舉手贊成給予港人居英權，可惜。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HkuCDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HkuCDo.jpg&h=0332c694&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ebd607e35aacbd1c6026c82205c1b2c6013a9ab","tid":1495657,"uid":278283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"58000 signed"},{"pid":"e40cbf0da0374bab45922038e065e3de1823a51a","tid":1495657,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"BNO平權文宣方向<br />\n不過, 從7月開始, 英國輿論 &ndash; 從每日快報, 衛報, 觀察者, 甚至太陽報紛紛鼓吹<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>英國政府應給予BNO持有者BC身份</ins></strong></span>. 值得一提的是英國智庫Adam Smith Institute在8月15日出了一份名為Doing Our Duty的研究報告, 建議<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國政府應將BNO權利擴大至與BC同等</span></ins></strong>, 因為若BNO人成為BC, 這&rdquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>將會促使中國和平地行事</ins></strong></span>&rdquo; (p. 6), 香港人可以&rdquo;在自由的環境下生活, 而中國則失去一整代人,<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"> 英國會得到道德和物質上的勝利</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 7). 不只如此, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人&rdquo;人均收入高, 高學歷及具備專業技能, 對英國經濟會有實質益處</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 8). 最後, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國幫BNO升級可顯示英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo;</span></ins></strong> (p. 9). 這份報告暗示: a. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></ins></strong>, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就行) (結論1和3); b. 英國對香港的&rdquo;道義和責任&rdquo;乃建基在利益上, 尤其<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">正值英國脫歐, 香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員</span></ins></strong> (結論2)."},{"pid":"f097ef8afd5818d9f17cec4572c318649a405a61","tid":1495657,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:46:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGITRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=8fa8afe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80f839d325622b32e8cda133072798ddf695e11","tid":1495657,"uid":158806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T22:16:31.000Z","msg":"其實加拿大，澳州，美國至係港人移民首選，記得英國推出居英權計劃，俾5萬個名額香港家庭，反應一般，俾的英國傳媒嘲笑"},{"pid":"ced968fc0406967806d60177c143ba298892d5bb","tid":1495657,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T22:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4903e12992b54b4f02573b721f6a7429af866a","tid":1495657,"uid":33933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T22:35:17.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f825ca24087b351e6a7ae2b41b22b8589fb71c3f","tid":1495657,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e40cbf0d